Disk World creator help
tell_zones

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
tell_zones -  This method displays a message in all the currently loaded rooms within the specified zone(s).
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
varargs void tell_zones(mixed zones,
string message,
mixed mess_class)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^zones%^RESET%^ - a zone name as a string, or an array of zone names
%^BOLD%^message%^RESET%^ - the message to be displayed
%^BOLD%^mess_class%^RESET%^ - the message type. Normally this need not be specified
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/room/inherit/terrain_map/handler_base.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method displays a message in all the currently loaded rooms
within the specified zone(s).
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
query_rooms_in_zone, tell_feature

.EP

